    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
      "name": "Blind Fight",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The corpse orgy doesn't need to succeed at a flat check to target @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed} creatures and is not @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed} to creatures that are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Hidden]{Hidden} from it. The corpse orgy needs only a successful @Check[type:flat|dc:5] to target a hidden creature. While the corpse orgy is adjacent to an undetected creature of its level or lower, it is instead only hidden from the corpse orgy.</p>"
        },
