    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
      "name": "Pain Shriek",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The corpse orgy unleashes a piercing shriek from the various heads captured in its form that deals [[/r {15d6}[sonic]]]{15d6 sonic damage} (@Check[type:fortitude|dc:32|basic:true]) in a @Template[type:burst|distance:40].</p>\n<p>Creatures with the @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Deafened]{Deafened} condition or cannot hear are not affected by Pain Shriek.</p>\n<p>The corpse orgy can't use Pain Shriek again for [[/r 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
        },
